    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work to be roadworthy. The engine struggles to maintain an idle and there are noticeable issues with the transmission shifting properly. Additionally, the body shows signs of rust and the interior has seen heavy wear over the years. This car is ideal for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts, and it is sold strictly as-is.",
